Package: mermaid2drawml
Type: Package
Title: Convert Mermaid Diagrams to Editable Word Shapes
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Author", "Name", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "author@example.com")
Description: Converts Mermaid flowchart diagrams to editable Microsoft Word
    shapes using the DrawingML wps:wsp format. The resulting shapes are
    natively editable in Word and can be inserted into documents via the
    officer package, suitable for use in R Markdown workflows.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Imports:
    tibble (>= 3.2.0),
    igraph (>= 1.5.0),
    officer (>= 0.6.0),
    rlang (>= 1.1.0),
    jsonlite (>= 1.8.0)
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    xml2 (>= 1.3.0),
    knitr,
    rmarkdown
Config/testthat/edition: 3
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
VignetteBuilder: knitr
